{"tid":1721263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉里單野 希望大家唔好比人帶風向","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:54:07.000Z","uid":87295,"like":151,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5f10fba88e6f3412d185f99f671938d84dc106","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係現職嘉里員工，做左十年。<br />\n今次想借朋友連登ac去澄清返之前話&rdquo;曾經高層&rdquo;所講ge野係假。<br />\n<br />\n1) 成棟嘉里貨運中心(簡稱KCC)有D層數係 嘉里物流自己用返，其餘係租比客。因為有外倉ge關係，D𨋢無&rdquo;曾經高層&rdquo;所講會咁早鎖。<br />\n<br />\n2) 抱歉無P1 floorplan，大家睇返1樓floorplan做參考，KCC的確係有3部𨋢，黑衫男士入ge係1號𨋢，佢出5樓都係1號𨋢 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYCQu04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYCQu04.jpg&h=3db1f6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DgxJk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DgxJk6.jpg&h=6e152b27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0BmBGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0BmBGa.jpg&h=baac9fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 你睇CCTV佢入電梯大堂隔離係車路，唔似盡頭，但大家上google map就見到其實KCC頭4層兩邊都有direct ramp access，但floorplan只係顯示左通到上1至15樓ge direct ramp access<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urC5iUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FurC5iUH.jpg&h=1055d0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 另外P1上一樓之後，其實車路已經反方向，所以你地睇到P1好似係中間部𨋢，但佢5樓出黎係尾𨋢咁。　但其實由頭到尾，佢都係搭緊1號𨋢。<br />\n<br />\n5) 有人會話點解得幾個人都聽唔到或者認唔出外來人，做倉好多散工真係唔會認得曬所有人；同埋其實就算係半夜，只要有人搬野/開剷車都會好嘈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚呢個&rdquo;曾經高層&rdquo;有咩目的要咁講，如果真係前高層無可能會搞錯D𨋢ge位置。<br />\n<br />\n我明白警謊好多野都唔可信，呢幾個月咁多單&rdquo;自殺案&rdquo;都全部無可疑，但講真如果係佢地做，尋晚可能已經封左樓。<br />\n<br />\n其實公司已經好好，罷工後無被秋後算帳，出面有事會比我地早走，返唔到唔會逼我地。我唔想被人覺得公司同員工係藍絲。大家體諒佢係一間上市公司，唔可以太出面表態。<br />\n<br />\n每日都有咁多人出入P1，其實搭一轉𨋢就知。同埋如果我有講大話，相信好快有同事、散工、租客、同送貨司機會提出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好比人帶風向，仲有好多手足要我地去幫手。"},{"pid":"ab15f68e65a38fb4f2a85a2b6c46d6e72388f26b","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"791f350d1241801a78c847223b234569d27fc106","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"ca784bcadef85f9a0d6e64e33a27894efd3334b0","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fd012b29dcd1f832c4f5713fdbc2776382b3f6","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"25837eebf03f3dbd81c9bab1d2fdf12c2055d806","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"反抗"},{"pid":"cf15cd63effa659ef7054197d6182a7d83027f2a","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0e4979fd86231869a6279859da38adb3ef9570e","tid":1721263,"uid":190793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61a9ec35056977127072f8d1c848e96f579f0afc","tid":1721263,"uid":140145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"651decc45b8540572bd622f81fc8db2413020743","tid":1721263,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2e33e102de9bcab081ae85321f2413dba54bb3","tid":1721263,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r