g":"11月14日中午講完, 同時360股價爆升<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6CtgYa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6CtgYa.png&h=e2438276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謹此向優品360 發出聲明，能完成以下要求，保證以後生日蒸蒸日上<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719169</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRL6N4E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRL6N4E.png&h=f959afbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqOg0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqOg0h.jpg&h=6ffbee5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連續半日升到爆, 今日升左20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我僅代表福建幫多謝連登左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一支汽水換回股價大回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人親手救360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登不代表我 裝修與否 前線決定！我地共同理念是攬炒！</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ewnpLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ewnpLS</a>"},{"pid":"ef223f1fefc3d40b6293328dc3a6d7c3dc29c83d","tid":1721263,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"thx"},{"pid":"aea0fd369b807e8f4a7263b82d5083892943636f","tid":1721263,"uid":197286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a78eca1aa5ea1eed3f3fcf7e6923f559920fecce","tid":1721263,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"d6658d8891611792072845e3f0003d682042c6a1","tid":1721263,"uid":236472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:41:54.000Z","msg":